I mean.

00:20:09.876 --> 00:20:13.838 position:50% align:center
You somehow manage to call Ami
by her first name, don't you?

00:20:13.922 --> 00:20:15.548 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:15.632 --> 00:20:18.301 position:50% align:center
I've known you for a pretty
long time now, you know.

00:20:18.385 --> 00:20:20.053 position:50% align:center
And I get, "Hey, you."

00:20:20.136 --> 00:20:22.889 position:50% align:center
Rude way to be,
don't you think?

00:20:22.972 --> 00:20:24.265 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:28.978 --> 00:20:31.439 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
I see. I was clueless.

00:20:31.523 --> 00:20:34.192 position:50% align:center
I didn't even realize
I'd made you feel bad.

00:20:36.111 --> 00:20:38.988 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry. For real.

00:20:39.072 --> 00:20:40.949 position:50% align:center
Huh?

00:20:41.032 --> 00:20:43.910 position:50% align:center
But, uh. I've always
been uncomfortable.

00:20:43.993 --> 00:20:47.414 position:50% align:center
With, like, using girls'
first names.

00:20:47.497 --> 00:20:49.416 position:50% align:center
Ami told me to call
her that for work,

00:20:49.499 --> 00:20:52.627 position:50% align:center
so I'm doing my best.

00:20:52.711 --> 00:20:56.172 position:50% align:center
Please, just... not that, okay?

00:20:56.256 --> 00:20:59.217 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI giggles]
Yeah, it's fine.

00:20:59.300 --> 00:21:01.052 position:50% align:center
I mean, I don't want to
force you or anything,

00:21:01.136 --> 00:21:02.679 position:50% align:center
mister gloomy-head.

00:21:02.762 --> 00:21:04.389 position:50% align:center
[grunting]

00:21:04.472 --> 00:21:06.099 position:50% align:center
Thanks for that.

00:21:08.727 --> 00:21:10.812 position:50% align:center
Still, hypnotizing with
a five-yen coin

00:21:10.895 --> 00:21:14.315 position:50% align:center
in this day and age?
No way was that gonna work.

00:21:14.399 --> 00:21:15.025 position:50% align:center
Right?

00:21:15.108 --> 00:21:17.235 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Uh...

00:21:17.318 --> 00:21:19.279 position:50% align:center
It worked?! Are you
kidding me right now?

00:21:19.362 --> 00:21:22.699 position:50% align:center
You must have zero
resistance or something!

00:21:22.782 --> 00:21:25.076 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Uh...

00:21:25.160 --> 00:21:26.453 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
How do I fix her?

00:21:26.536 --> 00:21:28.413 position:50% align:center
C'mon, it's gotta be
in here somewhere!

00:21:28.496 --> 00:21:29.497 position:50% align:center
Uzaki!

00:21:29.581 --> 00:21:32.500 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Uzaki is floating to the sky.

00:23:05.385 --> 00:23:07.262 position:50% align:center
[ASAI]
It isn't working.

00:23:07.345 --> 00:23:09.055 position:50% align:center
Look, what are you
talking about?

00:23:09.139 --> 00:23:11.725 position:50% align:center
I already told you,
I wasn't hypnotized!

00:23:11.808 --> 00:23:13.852 position:50% align:center
It's frightening that
you can't remember.

00:23:13.935 --> 00:23:15.687 position:50% align:center
I was never hypnotized.

00:23:15.770 --> 00:23:18.857 position:50% align:center
Trust me, it would be a big deal
for me if I actually was!

00:23:18.940 --> 00:23:21.067 position:50% align:center
Okay, but why do you
sound ticked off?

00:23:21.151 --> 00:23:23.194 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
I am not ticked off.

00:23:23.278 --> 00:23:25.280 position:50% align:center
[ASAI]
Dad. Could it be?

00:23:25.363 --> 00:23:26.489 position:50% align:center
[CAFÉ OWNER]
Yep.

00:23:26.573 --> 00:23:28.491 position:50% align:center
They say it's impossible
to hypnotize someone

00:23:28.575 --> 00:23:30.910 position:50% align:center
unless they trust
you completely.

00:23:30.994 --> 00:23:33.538 position:50% align:center
Which means these two...

00:23:33.621 --> 00:23:36.249 position:50% align:center
[ASAI]
It certainly does look that way.

00:23:37.417 --> 00:23:39.294 position:50% align:center
[CAFEÉ OWNER, ASAI]
Let's not tell 'em. This is fun.

00:23:39.377 --> 00:23:41.338 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI] If I were ticked off,
I think you'd know it.

00:23:41.421 --> 00:23:43.715 position:50% align:center
[SAKURAI]
Whatever! You totally are!

00:23:46.092 --> 00:23:48.470 position:50% align:center
[UZAKI]
Hey, what should we do next?